{"TopicId":204541,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Possible Forum Account Changes","CreatedByName":"Spaceman.Spiff","CreatedById":209133,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-27T18:15:35Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Spaceman.Spiff","CreatedById":209133,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-27T18:15:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u201C\u003Cstrong style=\u0022color:#2d3134;font-size:13px;\u0022\u003EWhat will happen to my forum account?\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr style=\u0022color:#2d3134;font-size:13px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:13px;\u0022\u003EYour forum account will remain a separate login from your Private Division Account. We are exploring opportunities to allow you to login to the forum and other places using your Private Division Account credentials in the near future. If anything changes regarding your existing forum login credentials, we will let you know in advance.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u201D\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nIn an announcement a few minutes ago this bit was included.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat are all your thoughts on this?\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nAre you in favor? Are you opposed?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI for one am not a huge fan of my forum account being attached to another account.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StarSlay3r","CreatedById":209403,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-27T20:14:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/209133-spacemanspiff/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022209133\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/209133-spacemanspiff/\u0022 id=\u0022ips_uid_5786_7\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Spaceman.Spiff\u003C/a\u003E! I set up a separate Kerbal Account discussion thread over here:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsEmbed_finishedLoading\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022209403\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed8713335491\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/204741-changes-to-your-kerbal-account-discussion-thread/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022overflow: hidden; height: 194px; max-width: 500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nso I\u0027ll be locking this thread. Please feel free to bring up this subject there though!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}